      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Convert Your Thrift Store Website Into a Mobile App</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Learn how to keep up with modern consumer expectations by converting your thrift store website into amazing native mobile apps with MobiLoud.</p>
